In `partitioned_function_ops.cc`, could you please wrap `TF_CHECK_OK` around both your `AddFunctionLibrary` calls (and make sure the formatting is ok)?
Line 105,
```c++
TF_CHECK_OK(
            graph.get()->AddFunctionLibrary(global_flib.ToProto()));
```
Line 261,
```c++
TF_CHECK_OK(
          subgraph.get()->AddFunctionLibrary(global_flib.ToProto()));
```
Thank you!
